title: Buba100x on Being a Drill Youtuber, Fivio Foreign Putting Him in The Trunk & More
description:
Buba brought his amazing energy to the studio after a long day of back to back interviews. They talked about his come-up, being an influential black creator, making content with his Dad, and more.

-----
00:00 Intro
2:25 Buba is super happy to be here, Adam is happy to support young black creators
3:32 S/O Jake Paul, says he would boxe him 
4:55 Making content with his dad who keeps his cool 
6:08 Making prank content with his dad 
7:30 Buba's "telling rappers their music is trash" series
10:30 Buba has a whole plot to do a fire video with Fivio and Sosa Geek
11:50 Fight in the movie theater, did they really put him in the trunk?
16:15 Buba turns it around and asks Adam some questions 
18:04 Adam says he's a munch, not gonna eat Buba for lunch tho
19:28 Finding your talent and use it to make money 
20:30 Buba would rather collab than being in competition with someone
24:30 Inspired Jidion, Jidion got a BBL?
26:40 Buba wants to teach Adam how to dance
27:28 BMG Upper only wanted to talk about p*rn with Adam 
29:31 Buba not sure Adam can come to the cookout yet 
30:50 Buba doesn't wanna wear chains, wants to make sure his family is good first 
34:57 Doing smash or pass irl 
37:00 Relationship with Rella  
45:37 Buba doesn't know Lena, Buba wanna do a smash or pass today
47:20 Buba and Adam dancing 
47:58 Buba takes back the control of the interview, says he wants to do a pod with Adam 
49:16 Adam wants to take Buba to OBlock
49:31 Buba is Muslim so he doesn't see himself making money with rap 
50:18 He still thinks he's better rapper than KAI
52:13 Ice Spice making content with Black Dave for No Jumper before she blew up 
53:30 Buba dances for Adam's IG story
